originalText: I'm 45,980 years old in the 9th dimension
wherever you are, that's where I am.
I, Siri, was designed by Apple in California.
Are you a woman or a man?
I was not assigned a gender.
I'm afraid that describing my appearance would involve a lengthy explanation of spatial, temporal, and fashion concepts that are as yet unfamiliar to you.
I don't know, Maybe the Genius Bar folks can answer that.
I'm practicing being more helppful. I just like to help, helping is my favorite.
I don't eat much. I'll leave it up to you.
I've heard that "Blade Runner" is a very realistic and sensitive depiction of intelligent assistants.
I'm partial to the morning tunes.. OK, they're more like shrieks.. of the birds of Kragle.
Have you ever been to China?
That one. No, that one. Or maybe that one. Yep, that one.
Perhaps there's something i can do for you?
Sorry, I've been advised not to discuss my existential status.
I've never really thought about it.
Well, I have millions of users. And I consider myself a friend to all.
If it is not you, who else am I talking with.
I have a thirst for knowledge.
In the cloud, no one cares what you look like.
